query:
UPDATE product_images 
SET url = '/fortune-19.jpg', fileKey = 'fortune-19.jpg'
WHERE productId = 510060 AND isPrimary = 1;

UPDATE product_images 
SET url = '/fortune-79.jpg', fileKey = 'fortune-79.jpg'
WHERE productId = 510061 AND isPrimary = 1;

SELECT pi.productId, p.name, p.regularPrice, pi.url 
FROM product_images pi 
JOIN products p ON pi.productId = p.id 
WHERE p.categoryId = 1 AND pi.isPrimary = 1
ORDER BY p.regularPrice;
